lead_paragraph: Arnold Palmer, one of golf's greatest players whose immense popularity drew a legion of fans to the game at the dawn of the age of televised sport, died of heart complications on Sunday. He was 87.

headline.print_headline: Golfing Great Arnold Palmer, Who Led 'Arnie's Army,' Dies at 87
